  "title": "Medical Research Nurse ( $30/hr ) #HCT",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><p>•\tProvides assistance to the research team</p><p>•\tScreens and recruits suitable patients to participate in the research project</p><p>•\tBriefs patients on research background and rationale and to obtain their consent of participation</p><p>•\tCollects data from patients' medical records and research statistics</p><p>•\tHelps document adverse events / reactions that arise</p><p>•\tPerforms phlebotomy and venepuncture when required</p><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><p>•\tMinimum Degree/ Diploma in Nursing</p><p>•\tMin 3 years’ experience in Hospital</p><p>Only Nurses with SNB license NEED APPLY</p><p></p><p>Interested candidates please send a copy of your resume in MS Word to</p><p><u><strong>Clinicalresearch@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></u></p><p></p><p></p><p>Cameron Tan</p><p>Outsourcing Team</p><p>Company Reg. No. 199601303W</p><p>EA Licence No. 99C4599</p>",
